queries.sql: SELECT `counseling_sessions`.*, `students`.`nisn`, `students`.`nis`, `users`.`full_name` as `student_name`, `classes`.`class_name`, `counselor_users`.`full_name` as `counselor_name`, (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM session_notes WHERE session_notes.session_id = counseling_sessions.id AND session_notes.deleted_at IS NULL) as note_count FROM `counseling_sessions` LEFT JOIN `students` ON `students`.`id` = `counseling_sessions`.`student_id` LEFT JOIN `users` ON `users`.`id` = `students`.`user_id` LEFT JOIN `classes` ON `classes`.`id` = `counseling_sessions`.`class_id` LEFT JOIN `users` as `counselor_users` ON `counselor_users`.`id` = `counseling_sessions`.`counselor_id` WHERE `counseling_sessions`.`counselor_id` = 15 AND `counseling_sessions`.`deleted_at` IS NULL ORDER BY `counseling_sessions`.`session_date` DESC, `counseling_sessions`.`session_time` DESC
